{"tid":802790,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果繼續落去會有抑鬱？","createTime":"2018-09-01T17:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T11:27:46.000Z","uid":61610,"like":52,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"adaa44f007190cc7b5237ebe9f664e54d242649b","tid":802790,"uid":61610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"有少少長<br />\r\n<br />\r\n是咁的，我有一個拍咗拖九年嘅男朋友<br />\r\n佢29歲，戶口4位數字都唔知有無<br />\r\n早兩年賭錢差人十幾萬，問啲邦民借咗差唔多十萬<br />\r\n<br />\r\n翻工 一星期遲到就必然嘅 心情唔好就一日早走<br />\r\n成日借啲二話呢到痛個到痛扮病唔翻工 <br />\r\n一唔順意就裸辭 隔個幾月先慢慢搵工<br />\r\n<br />\r\n屋企壞電器無錢買<br />\r\n兩個月我加加埋埋已經借咗萬8比佢周轉<br />\r\n<br />\r\n翻到屋企所有家務我做哂 <br />\r\n買餸煮飯洗碗一條龍服務<br />\r\n而佢就食雞、睇Facebook、睇波再食雞<br />\r\n有時仲比說話我聽 「點解拖完地都無乾淨過？」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n每日都嘈「鬧鐘響足兩個鐘都唔願起身」<br />\r\n「啲嘢周圍放」、「打少陣機得唔得」<br />\r\n呢三個輪迴問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n叫佢刪咗啲馬會app，係你兜口兜面即刻刪咗<br />\r\n但係第2日都可以見住佢仲用緊嚟睇波<br />\r\n<br />\r\n琴日刪第二次，岩岩又發現個app憑空出現<br />\r\n佢仲可以聲大夾惡問「你以為你邊位」「睇波都唔撚睇得？」「咁撚叻咪搬走囉」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n呢一刻我真係好失望，每次一嘈<br />\r\n我個心就好似比舊石壓住咁<br />\r\n我開始覺得自己有少少抑鬱<br />\r\n<br />\r\n永遠想決絕都決絕唔到<br />\r\n但係長期落去我應該會有精神病<br />\r\n<br />\r\n好多謝你睇到呢到，因為講出嚟個心會舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1721985d275844d778ae44deaa93aaa02f00c57","tid":802790,"uid":205419,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:05:28.000Z","msg":"分手囉"},{"pid":"f2d2f6ac8277d0be8387dee8c8e89d62817f8490","tid":802790,"uid":156130,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:05:53.000Z","msg":"點解佢咁都有女朋友而我冇，公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dde377635d9041039be3f3576b6a95130d4ffb3","tid":802790,"uid":197450,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:07:48.000Z","msg":"放過自己"},{"pid":"ab10a64192338e46b77ca697b3384d4ca2aab153","tid":802790,"uid":61610,"like":1,"dislike":31,"score":-30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:11:01.000Z","msg":"同居咗4年 話分邊有咁易....."},{"pid":"1444ca94e07b04630d18f4d84de9e94c8ab9b50e","tid":802790,"uid":48632,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:12:51.000Z","msg":"放過自己啦 咁落去真係好咩<br />\n佢都不求上進 你幫得佢幾多次？<br />\n雖然9年好難話斷就斷 但襯仲未嘥更多嘅時間 斬攬啦 試吓搬走先<br />\n要記住 你值得更好"},{"pid":"8d776119a0f33eb1589d40f5375c7811c7fea873","tid":802790,"uid":189703,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"爛賭男人不能要"},{"pid":"2f1c5221af811948f373fd0a7226d58fbce66b1c","tid":802790,"uid":1517,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:15:24.000Z","msg":"其實佢咁嘅生活方式冇問題，佢開心就好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果佢係一支公的話</span></span>"},{"pid":"5f1ea68c9f45213edfc3449652a0eb87391661eb","tid":802790,"uid":4412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:18:20.000Z","msg":"有咩令你留戀呢?"},{"pid":"16db1ad2519cbb65250cd80befef0f3edba4a38e","tid":802790,"uid":187116,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"打到咁大篇缺點<br />\n都仲可以未分手<br />\n個男人比左咩藥你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放過自己啦樓主<br />\n唔合適就灑脫啲<br />\n傷心就肯定架啦 拍左咁多年<br />\n但人生咁長 慢慢就會放低<br />\n咁既男人唔通對過世咩<br />\n感覺你都係個好既女朋友<br />\n何必拿住舊屎唔放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbba823cdd47df3bdf5857a2a59809194d96102","tid":802790,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab10a64192338e46b77ca697b3384d4ca2aab153","tid":802790,"uid":61610,"like":1,"dislike":31,"score":-30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:11:01.000Z","msg":"同居咗4年 話分邊有咁易....."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:20:01.000Z","msg":"唔好浪費自己時間啦<br />\n睇落佢都唔愛你"},{"pid":"47c3b765074d8f8684e5fbc52c551279eafd3c35","tid":802790,"uid":195515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:20:05.000Z","msg":"你會決絕到 未係時候姐"},{"pid":"cf970b002985cb2914f310c019757dc1ab014a25","tid":802790,"uid":61610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:26:26.000Z","msg":"可惜佢唔覺得我好<br />\n佢身邊啲豬朋狗友成日同佢講 唔好比飽飯啲女人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cad6fabb8843c487e375a548fd9f272b4c7e344","tid":802790,"uid":203889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:26:53.000Z","msg":"人生有幾多個十年<br />\n你就黎花左十分一時間係呢條友身上<br />\n你得到d咩？你既青春唔係咁樣羅黎浪費"},{"pid":"42c465e7bb133dd959a831d2da6e439ff8aef192","tid":802790,"uid":68478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:35:11.000Z","msg":"咁你想點？"},{"pid":"9d7af0f0e65bc575a2a1ccc0921df5f2eae0cf7f","tid":802790,"uid":195858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:42:37.000Z","msg":"咁都有女朋友仲同居4年<br />\n<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"482c550cba98293e5ad8e33356df5f0f424555ac","tid":802790,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:59:04.000Z","msg":"分手囉"},{"pid":"4c7512d0b73492ac8e801cbb1579e9c115332841","tid":802790,"uid":140662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:00:04.000Z","msg":"其實你自己都有答案啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da06ddcbacbf8a66606a2ef862777479d8e95f2b","tid":802790,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T23:53:52.000Z","msg":"何苦守著一個不愛你的人？<br />\n我愛不起不愛我的人，我的青春也愛不起。我的微笑、我的眼淚、我的深情、我年輕的日子，只為我愛也愛我的那個人浪擲。"},{"pid":"51a694c7425695810cf196e700f9ecdf540a1833","tid":802790,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T23:56:30.000Z","msg":"同居 租定點？"},{"pid":"57523235f0694244ca30831e0db6164e8c163465","tid":802790,"uid":127564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf970b002985cb2914f310c019757dc1ab014a25","tid":802790,"uid":61610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:26:26.000Z","msg":"可惜佢唔覺得我好<br />\n佢身邊啲豬朋狗友成日同佢講 唔好比飽飯啲女人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T00:09:17.000Z","msg":"屌 咁佢咁唔珍惜咁唔欣賞嘅 就斬佢老母條纜啦⋯<br />\n你忍撚倒9年呢條咁嘅廢人都幾撚勁<br />\nSor 見倒呢種男人真係唔撚屌唔撚鳩得<br />\n樓主 警方呼籲 及早放手"},{"pid":"687c50225961c669affaa9e0dfc69012ae83f535","tid":802790,"uid":193870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T00:12:57.000Z","msg":"佢想過佢既生活，你又逼佢過你想佢過既生活，既然兩個人既價值觀都唔同既，何苦呢？<br />\n<br />\n係一生人黎講，9年其實無你想像中咁長，放手或者可以擁有更多。"},{"pid":"daf4b59e188915fc836ecb45e4df4475425239f6","tid":802790,"uid":61610,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"687c50225961c669affaa9e0dfc69012ae83f535","tid":802790,"uid":193870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T00:12:57.000Z","msg":"佢想過佢既生活，你又逼佢過你想佢過既生活，既然兩個人既價值觀都唔同既，何苦呢？<br />\n<br />\n係一生人黎講，9年其實無你想像中咁長，放手或者可以擁有更多。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T00:24:13.000Z","msg":"其實我只係想佢勤力啲翻工，唔好遲到早退<br />\n一個月儲到5千咁嘅正常人生活<br />\n真係咁難咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04053696b4b1681952b1ecff84ccdd9c77ed4af2","tid":802790,"uid":61610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51a694c7425695810cf196e700f9ecdf540a1833","tid":802790,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T23:56:30.000Z","msg":"同居 租定點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T00:25:08.000Z","msg":"租嘅"},{"pid":"6436f61bbbd5cc47b7e570b7afe156b7c91ebb76","tid":802790,"uid":125515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T03:33:41.000Z","msg":"你幫唔到佢，因為佢做緊自己想做嘅事，可能有朝一日佢自己生性，自己幫自己<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，你唔幫自己，冇人幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5bf1577c2b967ccb50854c5a595f91f77bbc84","tid":802790,"uid":32219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04053696b4b1681952b1ecff84ccdd9c77ed4af2","tid"