,"uid":171119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T04:31:21.000Z","msg":"佢唔係威脅到你既話，將自己慢慢抽離佢，最後先搬走啦，咁落去無結果"},{"pid":"2d96c1612733faa36cf49a5435961bf12acc0af1","tid":802790,"uid":127705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T04:31:56.000Z","msg":"佢唔珍惜你點解要珍惜佢？<br />\n你太重視佢，佢唔會理你的<br />\n愛人先要愛自己，覺得傷心就走啦<br />\n我明白咁多年你會好唔捨得<br />\n你睇方力申同鄧麗欣拍左十年拖都分手<br />\n依家鄧麗欣都揾到個愛佢既人，過得幾幸福<br />\n有時要放手，先會得到更好"},{"pid":"2e623aa516e2f5328a356385af2cb131a4d99616","tid":802790,"uid":180348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5aefc39291adf38c31292f91e1139962b2d27458","tid":802790,"uid":130060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T04:22:39.000Z","msg":"點解d咁廢ge人都有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T04:32:17.000Z","msg":"竹門對竹門 木門對木門"},{"pid":"032ca7322f83a60efd94181fdc441221025d3cd6","tid":802790,"uid":17088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:12:20.000Z","msg":"分手啦on9<br />\n呢啲垃圾有撚用"},{"pid":"b4c3667c20c60d976cda5fafe416f1ac4c289b0e","tid":802790,"uid":195975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"覺得自己係零<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd78666fc5c7e8464435c942c6138d586107aa5","tid":802790,"uid":123308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"sunk cost 沉沒成本<br />\n<br />\n如果前面成本唔計，你仲會唔會揀呢個人？<br />\n相信 rational 答案已經好明顯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好畀 sunk cost 影響決定，無限向負數溝淡"},{"pid":"3b72145710eec23e9e8de86720469c1b719972ed","tid":802790,"uid":92690,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05